column16: Danny Santana grounds into a double play, first baseman Adam Lind to shortstop Jose Reyes.   Kurt Suzuki out at 2nd.
Eduardo Nunez lines out to right fielder Steve Tolleson.
Kurt Suzuki singles on a line drive to left fielder Melky Cabrera.
Kendrys Morales doubles (3) on a line drive to center fielder Anthony Gose.   Danny Santana scores.    Eduardo Escobar scores.    Joe Mauer scores.
Josh Willingham pops out to third baseman Brett Lawrie on the infield fly rule.
Joe Mauer walks.   Danny Santana to 3rd.    Eduardo Escobar to 2nd.
Eduardo Escobar singles on a bunt ground ball to third baseman Brett Lawrie.   Danny Santana to 2nd.
Danny Santana singles on a ground ball to second baseman Steve Tolleson.
Omar Infante grounds out, third baseman Juan Francisco to first baseman Edwin Encarnacion.
Jarrod Dyson grounds out, second baseman Brett Lawrie to first baseman Edwin Encarnacion.
Alcides Escobar grounds out, shortstop Jose Reyes to first baseman Edwin Encarnacion.
Danny Valencia flies out to left fielder Melky Cabrera.
